'''共和理工學院'''（{{lang-en|'''Republic Polytechnic'''}}，縮寫：RP）是[[新加坡|新加坡]]的一所[[理工學院|理工學院]]，是新加坡最早在所有科目中採用[[問題導向學習|問題導向學習]]的學校。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sundaytimes.lk/100516/Education/ed18.html |title=The Sunday Times: Education, Republic Polytechnic Singapore |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2020-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215000551/http://www.sundaytimes.lk/100516/Education/ed18.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/1055852/1/.html |title=Channel News Asia: Republic Polytechnic Sees its Fifth and Largest Batch of Graduates |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2012-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022081442/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/1055852/1/.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

