2007年7月31日，共和理工學院的[[兀蘭|兀蘭]]校區由新加坡總理[[李顯龍|李顯龍]]揭幕，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rp.sg/pmopening/ |title=Official Opening Ceremony of Republic Polytechnic |access-date=2013-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080628095740/http://www.rp.sg/pmopening/ |archive-date=2008-06-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 校區建築是由日本建築師[[槙文彦|槙文彦]]設計的，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.maki-and-associates.co.jp/e/project/43.html |title=Maki and Associates: Architecture and Planning |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2011-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110503231249/http://www.maki-and-associates.co.jp/e/project/43.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2006年完工，容量約為一萬三千名學生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.beca.com/projects/buildings/education/republic_polytechnic_singapore_2.aspx |title=BECA: Republic Polyechnic, Teaching Environment with Added Energy Efficiency |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2011-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707221000/http://www.beca.com/projects/buildings/education/republic_polytechnic_singapore_2.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2008年，該學院獲得[[ASEAN|ASEAN]]最佳實踐節能建築獎。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.news.gov.sg/public/sgpc/en/media_releases/agencies/ema/press_release/P-20100722-1/AttachmentPar/0/file/ASEAN%20Energy%20Awards.pdf |title=Singapore Bags 5 ASEAN Energy Awards BCA.gov.sg: Singapore Bags 5 ASEAN Energy Awards |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2011-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718072345/http://www.news.gov.sg/public/sgpc/en/media_releases/agencies/ema/press_release/P-20100722-1/AttachmentPar/0/file/ASEAN%20Energy%20Awards.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2009年11月，被新加坡環境理事會授予[[綠色建築|綠色建築]]稱號。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sec.org.sg/awards/ecooffice |title=Singapore Environment Council: Project Eco-office |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2011-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110903230908/http://www.sec.org.sg/awards/ecooffice |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ecoaction.sg/PastEcoAction2009.aspx |title=Past Eco Action Day |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2010-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100704174516/http://www.ecoaction.sg/PastEcoAction2009.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2010年又獲得總統設計獎。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.designsingapore.org/pda_public/gallery.aspx?sid=50 |title=DesignSingapore.org: President*s Design Award 2009 |access-date=2013-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029200733/http://www.designsingapore.org/pda_public/gallery.aspx?sid=50 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

